                                <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 cus-text" style="margin-top:1%;margin-bottom:1%;padding:0;">
                                    <h6 style="color:#492A7F;font-weight:700;"><span style="color:#ff0000;font-weight:800;">Note:-&nbsp;</span>Admission is Provisional subject to the Verification of Eligibility & Fee Amount by the College/University as per Norms</h6>
                                    <span style="color:#492A7F;"><strong>a. You will be given Provisional Admission in this course, subject to the verification of your eligibility in this course by the College/Affiliating University. In case of any discrepancy, the college is authorized to cancel the Provisional Admission of the student.</strong></span><br />
                                    <span style="color:#492A7F;"><strong>b. The college is authorized to take the short payment, if any discrepancy, from the student at later stage as per Affiliating University/State Government norms.</strong></span>

                                </div>

                                <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 text-right cus-text">
